From 9567d8cdec9bd05226f0ad49bb0ee3398b9dd5a4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Hardcore <hardcorgamingstyle@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Jul 2026 17:18:22 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] feat: overhaul desktop app UI + fix AuthDesktop auth
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Desktop app (.exe):
- Replace all 4 empty placeholder mode views (Chat, Build, Research, Study)
  with full premium WPF UI implementations
- ChatView: message bubbles, model pills (Sonnet/Opus/Haiku/Gemini),
  animated typing indicator, streaming SSE via StreamingClient
- Build/CodeView: 9-agent pipeline UI with live progress dots, code output,
  project brief header, green theme
- ResearchView: animated progress bar, example prompt chips, streaming output
- StudyView: tutor/quiz/solve/summary mode toggles, subject chips, purple theme
- MainWindow: replace emoji sidebar icons with clean vector Path geometries

Website:
- AuthDesktop.tsx: replace useAuthActions (Convex-native, broken) with
  custom OTP flow (useAction customAuth.sendOtp/verifyOtp) matching Auth.tsx
  — fixes desktop auth that was silently failing
